Drinking from the same cup. Husband and wife become one.

26
00:06:32,399 --> 00:06:35,111
Two hearts united, bringing everlasting happiness and prosperity.

27
00:06:46,759 --> 00:06:48,680
What else? Mother, what else?

28
00:06:50,000 --> 00:06:51,000
