85
00:13:08,080 --> 00:13:09,351
and give you this gift.

86
00:13:12,159 --> 00:13:13,630
It's not something important.

87
00:13:13,711 --> 00:13:15,419
Coincidentally, you've opened a new shop recently.

88
00:13:15,759 --> 00:13:17,559
