95
00:13:39,512 --> 00:13:40,630
and pair them with the pill.

96
00:13:41,440 --> 00:13:43,231
Won't that make us more money?

97
00:13:49,279 --> 00:13:51,390
Sandalwood can help reduce hair loss

98
